@PaymentsService_HostAddress = http://localhost:5037

GET {{PaymentsService_HostAddress}}/weatherforecast/
Accept: application/json

### PaymentsService API Tests

### 1. Get all payments (protected endpoint - requires authentication)
GET https://localhost:7003/payments
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_JWT_TOKEN_HERE
Accept: application/json

### 2. Get payment by ID (protected endpoint - requires authentication)
GET https://localhost:7003/payments/1
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_JWT_TOKEN_HERE
Accept: application/json

### 3. Create new payment (protected endpoint - requires authentication)
POST https://localhost:7003/payments
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_JWT_TOKEN_HERE
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "id": 0,
    "orderId": 104,
    "amount": 599.99,
    "paymentMethod": "Credit Card",
    "paymentDate": "2024-01-01T00:00:00",
    "status": "Pending"
}

### 4. Update payment status (protected endpoint - requires authentication)
PUT https://localhost:7003/payments/1/status?status=Completed
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_JWT_TOKEN_HERE

### 5. Get specific payment
GET https://localhost:7003/payments/2
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_JWT_TOKEN_HERE
Accept: application/json

### Note: Replace YOUR_JWT_TOKEN_HERE with actual JWT token from UsersService login
